testcase.assertions: [SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address7] - User agents can determine if this Address represents the 'wildcard' contact address.
testcase.name: testIsWildcard001

testcase.assertions: [SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address12] - User agents can get the String representation of this Address.
testcase.name: testToString001

testcase.assertions: [SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address8] - IllegalStateException should be thrown if this Address is used in a context where it cannot be modified
testcase.name: testSetDisplayName101

testcase.assertions: [SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address11] - IllegalStateException should be thrown if this Address is used in a context where it cannot be modified.
testcase.name: testSetURI101

testcase.assertions: [SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address11] - NullPointerException be thrown on null uri.
testcase.name: testSetURI102

testcase.assertions: [SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address10] - IllegalArgumentException should be thrown if the new qvalue isn't between 0.0 and 1.0 (inclusive) and isn't -1.0.
testcase.name: testSetQ101

testcase.assertions: [SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address2] - User agents can compare the given Address with this Address.
testcase.name: testEquals001

testcase.assertions: [SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address4][SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address9] - User agents can get and set 'Expires' parameter of this Address.
testcase.name: testGetSetExpires001

testcase.assertions: [SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address5][SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address10] - User agents can get and set 'q' parameter of this Address.
testcase.name: testGetSetQ001

testcase.assertions: [SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address6][SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address11] - User agents can get and set 'URI' of this Address.
testcase.name: testGetSetURI001

testcase.assertions: [SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address1] - User agents can get a clone of this Address.
testcase.name: testClone001

testcase.assertions: [SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address3][SipServlet:JAVADOC:Address8] - User agents can get and set 'DisplayName' parameter of this Address.
testcase.name: testGetSetDisplayName001
